  <id>com.kdbxstudio.KDBXStudio</id>
  <name>KDBXStudio</name>
  <summary>Modern Qt6 KDBX password manager for Linux</summary>
  <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
  <project_license>GPL-3.0-or-later</project_license>
  <developer_name>Cuma KURT</developer_name>
  <description>
    <p>
      KDBXStudio is an open-source KeePass-compatible password manager built with Qt6.
      It focuses on multi-database workspaces, password health audits, plugins, and a
      keyboard-first desktop experience.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>KDBX 4.x open/create/save with optional key files</li>
      <li>Password health dashboard and advanced search</li>
      <li>TOTP, attachments, certificates/SSH inspection</li>
      <li>Plugin marketplace for built-in extensions</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
